snippet.textDisplay:
SBS 당장 사과해 너네 때문에 우리 언니 다쳤고 너네는 그거 제대로 사과도 안 했잖아 웬디 언니 너네가 하자는 콜라보 무대 하려고 엄청 열심히 연습했고 그 열심히 연습한 무대 리허설 하다가 다친 거야 당장 사과해 광대, 골반, 손목이면 엄청 심하게 다친 거야 전치 6주라잖아 밥도 못 먹어 제대로 으깨서 먹거나 비지찌개 먹어 빨리 사과해 제대로

사과문 양식

들어가야 되는 것

1. 내가 누구인가
2. 본인이 언제 어디서 무슨 잘못을 어떻게 저질렀는가
3. 그래서 누구에게 피해를 끼쳤는가
4. 실제 상황과 다르게 알려진 사실이 있는가 (추락 지점 위치를 맨 처음에 2미터라고 했지만 알고 보니 2층 높이의 계단 무대장치)
5. 얼마나 반성하고 있는가
6. 앞으로 어떻게 책임질 것인가

들어가면 안 되는 것

1. 본의 아니게
2. 오해
3. 그럴 뜻은 없었지만
4. 억울합니다
5. 하지만 저의 잘못은 아닙니다
6. 그럴 의도는 아니였지만

Some fans paid so much to get there and they weren’t even let in...

#GetWellSoonWendy

snippet.textDisplay:
I’m going to try and give updates on Wendy for everybody :)

So what happened to Wendy?
She was instructed to walk through a tunnel (that was dark) to some stairs by staff. Except the stairs weren’t there and she fell 2.5m. She fractured her right wrist and hip, cracked her cheekbone and is obviously very bruised. Doctors have to wait for swelling to go down before they can completely assess the situation.

Any updates?
Yes, as of today’s fansign, the members have told us some things. Joy said she was also upset at the apology and was glad fans didn’t let it go, Wendy prepared really hard for her stage & didn’t even let go of the mic because she wanted to sing that badly. The members mentioned she cannot chew right now and that they have brought her drinks and things. Seulgi said they would have to promote as 4 and that we shouldn’t mind voice cracks and things. The members apparently watched the show live with Wendy in the hospital while Irene mced.

What can we do to help?
First of all, you could comment or message Wendy supportive messages. She is probably not able to read them yet but just showcasing your support and patience will mean a lot to her. Similarly you could do the same with the other members, as it’ll be hard on them too. If you’re able to, you could buy their new album and support them that way. If you’re in Korea and could go and support them physically, that would be great. If you’re like me and online, we can cheer loudly for all the other members every time they perform. And make sure we don’t let this issue get swept under the rug.

I’ll try and update when new information comes out :) if there’s anything I’m wrong or I missed, feel free to correct me.

Similarly you could do the same with the other members, as it’ll be hard on them too. If you’re able to, you could buy their new album and support them that way. If you’re in Korea and could go and support them physically, that would be great. If you’re like me and online, we can cheer loudly for all the other members every time they perform. And make sure we don’t let this issue get swept under the rug. 

I’ll try and update when new information comes out :) if there’s anything I’m wrong or I missed, feel free to correct me.
